children.label: Land regions
children.desc: Models that mainly related to land regions, includes hydrology, hydrodynamics, soil, landform, terrestrial ecosystem etc.

children.label: Ocean regions
children.desc: Models that mainly related to ocean regions, includes coastal, seawater, sea-ice, marine ecosystem etc.

children.label: Frozen regions
children.desc: Models that mainly related to frozen regions, includes galicer, permafrost, snow etc.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to atmospheric regions, includes climate, weather, air etc.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to space-earth regions, includes sun-earth, planets etc.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to development activities, includes continents, countries, cities, administrative zones etc.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to social activities, includes urban, rural, cultural area, travel area, built-up area, indoor area etc.

children.label: Economic activities
children.desc: Models that mainly related to economic activities, includes agriculture, industry, tourism, trasport, energy, markets etc.

children.label: Human-perspective
children.desc: Models that mainly related to human geography.

children.label: Integrated-perspective
children.desc: Models that integrate many different models.

children.desc: Integrated models that apply in global scale.

children.label: Regional scale
children.desc: Integrated models that apply in regional scale.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to geoinformation analysis, includes vector analysis, raster analysis, network analysis, topology analysis etc.

children.label: Remote sensing analysis
children.desc: Models that mainly related to remote sensing analysis, includes imagery analysis, spectrum analysis etc.

children.label: Geostatistical analysis
children.desc: Models that mainly related to geostatistical analysis, includes pattern detection, relation detection, clustering, interpolation etc.

children.label: Intelligent computation analysis
children.desc: Models that mainly related to intelligent computation analysis, includes machine learning, deep learning etc.

children.label: Data-perspective
children.desc: Models that mainly related to data process.

children.desc: Models that mainly related to physical process calculation, includes CFD, acoustic simulation, light simulation etc.

children.label: Chemical process calculation
children.desc: Models that mainly related to chemical process calculation, includes insecticide, photosynthesis, combustion etc.

children.label: Biological process calculation
children.desc: Models that mainly related to biological process calculation, includes genome, metabolic, cellular simulation etc.

children.label: Human-activity calculation
children.desc: Models that mainly related to human-activity calculation, includes monte carlo, CA, agent-based, travel, crime, disease, migration, health etc.
